  <name>SysD Manager</name>
  <summary>A GUI to manage systemd units</summary>
  <!--   <icon type="stock">io.github.plrigaux.sysd-manager</icon> -->
  <description>
    <p>Manage your Services, Timers, Sockets and other units. You can enable, disable, stop and
      start them. Also,
      you can view their config file and peak at their journal logs.
    </p>
  </description>
